Economic burden of long-term complications of deep vein thrombosis after total 
hip replacement surgery in the United States.

Caprini JA(1), Botteman MF, Stephens JM, Nadipelli V, Ewing MM, Brandt S, Pashos 
CL, Cohen AT.

Author information:
(1)Evanston Northwestern Healthcare, Evanston, IL, USA.

BACKGROUND: Estimates of the cost of long-term complications of a primary deep 
vein thrombosis (DVT), including the post-thrombotic syndrome (PTS) and 
recurrent venous thromboembolism (VTE), may be relevant for resource allocation 
